Can I give you just one word
of advice, Dimitri?

1015
01:17:43,534 --> 01:17:45,119
Listen, Dimitri.

1016
01:17:45,244 --> 01:17:48,747
Put everything you've got into those
two sectors and you can't miss!

1017
01:17:55,212 --> 01:17:58,799
Sir, if we continue to lose fuel
at the present rate...

1018
