1023
01:18:15,441 --> 01:18:17,735
I don't give a hoot in hell
how you do it...

1024
01:18:17,860 --> 01:18:19,904
...just get me to the primary,
you hear?

1025
01:18:20,404 --> 01:18:23,449
I'm sorry, sir,
but those are the figures.

1026
01:18:23,574 --> 01:18:26,785
We'll be lucky to reach
weather ship at Tango Delta.

1027
01:18:26,911 --> 01:18:28,996
Well, shoot!

1028
01:18:29,121 --> 01:18:32,917
We ain't come this far just
to dump this thing in the drink.

1029
