Sir, if the rate of loss
does not increase...

1031
01:18:47,139 --> 01:18:50,851
...we have a chance
to reach target 384...

1032
01:18:50,976 --> 01:18:55,773
...grid coordinate 003 691...

1033
01:18:55,898 --> 01:18:59,693
...and possibly make it from there
to the Tango Delta weather ship.

1034
01:18:59,818 --> 01:19:01,862
What kind of a target
is that, anyhow?

1035
01:19:01,987 --> 01:19:05,866
Sir, that's the ICBM
complex at Kotloss.

1036
01:19:05,991 --> 01:19:11,705
All right.
Designating new target: 384.

1037
01:19:11,830 --> 01:19:14,833
Give me a heading on that as soon
