1123
01:27:46,887 --> 01:27:49,389
It would be quite easy...

1124
01:27:51,725 --> 01:27:56,813
...at the bottom of some
of our deeper mineshafts.

1125
01:27:56,980 --> 01:28:01,777
The radioactivity would not penetrate
a mine some thousands of feet deep.

1126
01:28:01,902 --> 01:28:06,114
And in a matter of weeks, sufficient
improvements in dwelling space...

1127
01:28:06,239 --> 01:28:08,116
...could easily be provided.

1128
01:28:08,241 --> 01:28:10,619
