I'm sorry, Mr President.

1137
01:28:51,993 --> 01:28:55,747
Nuclear reactors could provide
power almost indefinitely.

1138
01:28:55,872 --> 01:28:58,667
Greenhouses could maintain
plant life.

1139
01:28:58,792 --> 01:29:02,212
Animals could be bred
and slaughtered.

1140
01:29:02,337 --> 01:29:04,339
A quick survey would have
to be made...

1141
01:29:04,464 --> 01:29:06,841
...of the available mine sites
in the country.

1142
01:29:07,008 --> 01:29:10,595
But I would guess
that a dwelling space...

1143
01:29:10,720 --> 01:29:14,432
...for several hundred thousand of
our people could easily be provided.

1144
01:29:14,558 --> 01:29:17,602
Well, I would hate
to have to decide...

1145
01:29:17,811 --> 01:29:20,605
...who stays up
and who goes down.

1146
01:29:20,730 --> 01:29:24,568
Well, that would not be necessary,
Mr President.

1147
01:29:24,693 --> 01:29:27,529
It could easily be accomplished
with a computer.

1148
01:29:27,654 --> 01:29:29,906
The computer could
be set and programmed...

1149
01:29:30,031 --> 01:29:33,034
...to accept factors
from youth, health...

1150
