Of course, it would be
absolutely vital...

1153
01:29:41,334 --> 01:29:45,255
...that our top government
and military men be included...

1154
01:29:45,380 --> 01:29:50,176
...to foster and impart the required
principles of leadership and tradition.

1155
01:29:56,057 --> 01:29:59,102
Naturally, they would breed
prodigiously.

1156
01:29:59,227 --> 01:30:03,064
There would be much time
and little to do.

1157
01:30:03,607 --> 01:30:08,486
But with the proper breeding
techniques and a ratio of, say...

1158
01:30:08,612 --> 01:30:11,323
...10 females to each male...

1159
01:30:11,489 --> 01:30:16,077
...they could then work their way back
to the present gross national product...

1160
01:30:16,202 --> 01:30:18,663
...within, say, 20 years.

1161
01:30:18,788 --> 01:30:23,501
But look here, doctor.
Wouldn't this nucleus of survivors...

1162
01:30:23,627 --> 01:30:27,005
...be so grief-stricken
and anguished that they'd...

1163
01:30:27,130 --> 01:30:30,592
...well, envy the dead
and not wanna go on living?

1164
01:30:30,717 --> 01:30:33,553
No, sir. Excuse me.

1165
01:30:42,604 --> 01:30:46,691
No, sir. When they go down into the
mine, everyone would still be alive.

1166
01:30:46,816 --> 01:30:48,860
There would be
no shocking memories...

1167
01:30:48,985 --> 01:30:53,615
...the prevailing emotion will be one
of nostalgia for those left behind...

1168
01:30:53,740 --> 01:30:59,955
...combined with a spirit of bold
curiosity for the adventure ahead!

