01:31:16,596 --> 01:31:18,556
Doctor...

1170
01:31:20,684 --> 01:31:26,147
...you mentioned the ratio
of 10 women to each man.

1171
01:31:26,272 --> 01:31:29,359
Now, wouldn't that necessitate
the abandonment...

1172
01:31:29,484 --> 01:31:33,196
...of the so-called
monogamous sexual relationship?

1173
01:31:33,321 --> 01:31:36,908
I mean, as far as men
were concerned?

1174
01:31:37,033 --> 01:31:38,368
Regrettably, yes.

1175
01:31:38,493 --> 01:31:43,748
But it is, you know, a sacrifice required
for the future of the human race.

1176
01:31:43,873 --> 01:31:49,546
I hasten to add that since each man
will be required to do prodigious...

1177
